who Pelletreau spoke to, what they discussed, or when the first
face-to-face talks might be arranged.
   Abu Yahia, director of the PLO political section, confirmed in a
telephone interview from Paris that the conversation took place but
declined to identify the PLO official who spoke with Pelletreau.
